      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"2. SUPREME QUEEN held a forward position from the pinch but drifted out of the finish when 7th at this track in a Grade 5. Solid record here at the distance winning four races. Should be very hard to beat this time. 3. SPECIAL PLAYERS is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 4 lengths at this track in a handy 23.01 beating Pay Up Sally. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Expected to measure up again. 8. WARRIOR PAGE was below best at her last start when 6th at this track following a win (23.10) there two back. Solid record here at the distance winning four races. Form is hard to fault from this box, with a win and two minor placings from three starts. Cannot be underestimated.\",\"runners\":[2,3,8],\"exclusive\":false}",
